    <string name="app_name">Companion Overlay</string>
    <string name="accessibility_service_description">Senni uses this to capture your screen when you long-press her (or when your Nexus companion server asks with your consent-configured token), and to detect volume-button shortcuts and keyboard visibility. Captures happen only when triggered and are sent to your own Nexus companion server to generate her response. Nothing is captured or recorded in the background.</string>

